                <p><b>How can I become a member?</b></p>
                  <p>Creating an account enrolls you in our Khaas tier. All purchases made, when signed in, are eligible for point accumulation.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="descsection">
                <p><b>Is there a membership fee to the program?</b></p>
                  <p>No, there are no fees to join the program.</p>
              </div>
               <div class="descsection">
                <p><b>How can I check my points balance?</b></p>
                  <p>Your points balance is available to view on your <a href="/pages/rewards/?loyal">program dashboard</a> (you must be signed in to your account to view your points balance).</p>
              </div>
            <div class="descsection">
                <p><b>Do my points expire?</b></p>
                  <p>Yes, your points expire one year from the date of you earning them.</p>
              </div>
               <div class="descsection">
                <p><b>How do I earn points?</b></p>
                  <p>Earn points on all your purchases – Khaas members earn 2 points for every Rs 100 spent while Shikhar members earn 5 points for every Rs 100 spent. In addition, earn:</p>
                 <ul>
