                   <li>100 points on your birthday each year</li>
                   <li>50 points when you follow us on social media</li>
                 </ul>	
              </div>
              <div class="descsection">
                <p><b>How do I redeem points?</b></p>
                  <p>Points can be redeemed on your program dashboard. Select one of our many rewards that can then be used at the time of completing your order.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="descsection">
                <p><b>Are there any products or conditions in which I can’t earn points?</b></p>
                  <p>You must be signed into your account at time of placing your order in order to earn points. You can earn points on all products except gift cards. Also, point accumulation and redemption is unavailable on certain times, such as during our annual sale, special promotions and events, etc.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="descsection">
                <p><b>Can I transfer my points to someone else?</b></p>
                  <p>No, points are exclusively for your use and cannot be transferred to anyone else.</p>
              </div>
